-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/patti-smith-hospital-italy-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/patti-smith-hospital-italy-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/patti-smith">，帕蒂·史密斯</a>因“突发疾病”被送往医院，因此被迫取消了本周在意大利的一场演出。</p><p>这位 76 岁的创作歌手原定于周二（12 月 12 日）在博洛尼亚的杜斯剧院演出，但演出在短时间内被取消。</p><p>据意大利新闻来源<em><a href="https://www.tgcom24.mediaset.it/spettacolo/patti-smith-malore-ricoverata-bologna_74337458-202302k.shtml" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TG Com 24</a></em>报道，史密斯生病后被送往博洛尼亚马焦雷医院接受观察。</p><p>杜斯剧院在一份已翻译成英文的新闻稿中写道：“我们非常遗憾地通知善良的观众，由于艺术家突发疾病，帕蒂·史密斯的音乐会将无法上台。”</p><p> “对于此消息给您带来的不便，我们深表歉意。我们衷心祝愿这位艺术家早日康复。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0uwUuAi1Yl/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none"